  "text": "Many antidepressants have been shown in randomised controlled trials to reduce binge eating and purging in patients with bulimia nervosa. Antidepressants also reduce concerns about body weight and shape and reduce symptoms of depression and anxiety. [CITATION_1] Tricyclic antidepressants, monoamine oxidase inhibitors, buproprion and SSRIs have all shown efficacy.",
